---
title: Mexican-Inspired Beyond Meat® Stew with Tortilla Chips
description: Packed with hearty Beyond Meat® and delicious veggies, this Mexican stew is the perfect remedy to a long work week. Crushed tortilla chips and a dollop of sour cream offer a pop of flavour, perfect for finishing off this bowl of goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-beyond-meat-a-la-mexicaine-45afb3c3.jpg
